HEADWORD: Underwriter
<hw>Un"der*writ`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
underwrites his name to the conditions of an insurance policy,
especially of a marine policy; an insurer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

